data.name: Quick Flatbread
data.quickTastyDescription: Simple and delicious flatbreads that are perfect for wraps or enjoying with dips.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a large mixing bowl, combine all-purpose flour, baking powder, and salt.
Add water and olive oil to the dry ingredients and mix until a dough forms.
Knead the dough on a floured surface for a minute until smooth.
Divide the dough into small balls and roll each one out into a thin circle.
Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat and cook each flatbread for 2-3 minutes on each side until lightly golden.
Serve warm or use for sandwiches and wraps.
